-- Bank of America Appoints Marcos Buscaglia as Chief Latin America Economist
-- Lester Pimentel
-- 2010-07-23T18:44:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/bank-of-america-appoints-marcos-buscaglia-as-chief-latin-america-economist.html

          
          
             Bank of America Corp. hired Marcos
Buscaglia as chief Latin America economist from Citigroup Inc.,
the Charlotte, North Carolina-based bank said in a memo.  
          
          


  


        